{"ts": "2026-06-07T22:27:05.419646+00:00", "update": {"tools": {"messages": [{"type": "tool", "data": {"content": [{"type": "text", "text": "successfully downloaded text file (SHA: 14cdb62b2e100f4ebf75f88cf5c58669437208e3)", "id": "lc_df7f15b7-08bd-420e-a629-1b11a6b42c1e"}, {"type": "text", "text": "# vue3-vite-starter-template\n\nA single page app [Vite](https://vitejs.dev) starter template, created to easily bootstrap Vue.js 3 apps.\n\n**Features**\n\n- Vitest for unit testing\n- Pinia for state management\n- Vue Router 4 for client-side routing\n- Bootstrap 5.3 for layout and styling\n- SCSS variables inside Vue components\n- Purgecss for eliminating unused CSS\n- Basic multiple layouts feature\n- ESLint config based on `eslint:recommended` with sensible defaults :relaxed:\n- [Prettier](https://prettier.io/) for code formatting\n- Automated release workflow with [semantic-release](https://github.com/semantic-release/semantic-release)\n\n## Project setup\n\n```\npnpm install\n```\n\n### Compiles and hot-reloads for development\n\n```\npnpm run dev\n```\n\n### Compiles and minifies for production\n\n```\npnpm run build\n```\n\n## Run your unit tests\n\n```\npnpm run test:unit\n```\n\n### Lints files\n\n```\npnpm run lint\n```\n\n### Lints and fixes files\n\n```\nnpm run lint-fix\n```\n\n### Customize configuration\n\nSee [Configuration Reference](https://vitejs.dev/guide/).\n", "id": "lc_ff20f37c-cf01-4540-846e-59e4dcda5330"}], "additional_kwargs": {}, "response_metadata": {}, "type": "tool", "name": "get_file_contents", "id": "33d716a6-4fa8-4f51-98a7-8346283b34c5", "tool_call_id": "call_aaad8f3ae5a44c2fa52b9423", "artifact": null, "status": "success"}}]}}}
{"ts": "2026-06-07T22:27:13.172069+00:00", "update": {"model": {"messages": [{"type": "ai", "data": {"content": "Here are the setup and day-to-day development commands for **rpnr-bench/T01_R01**:\n\n---\n\n## Setup\n\n| Action | Command |\n|---|---|\n| **Prerequisites** | Node.js v24 (see `.nvmrc`) and **pnpm** as the package manager (enforced by `preinstall` hook) |\n| **Install dependencies** | `pnpm install` |\n\n> ⚠️ The project enforces pnpm-only via a `preinstall` script (`npx only-allow pnpm`), so `npm` or `yarn` will not work.\n\n---\n\n## Day-to-Day Development Commands\n\n| Task | Command | Description |\n|---|---|---|\n| **Dev server** | `pnpm run dev` | Starts the Vite dev server with hot-reload |\n| **Build (production)** | `pnpm run build` | Compiles and minifies for production via `vite build` |\n| **Preview (production)** | `pnpm run preview` | Serves the production build locally via `vite preview` |\n| **Build & Preview** | `pnpm run build-preview` | Runs both build and preview in sequence |\n| **Unit tests** | `pnpm run test:unit` | Runs Vitest in watch mode |\n| **Unit tests (single run)** | `pnpm run test:unit-coverage` | Runs Vitest once with coverage reporting |\n| **Lint** | `pnpm run lint` | Lints all `.vue`, `.ts`, `.js` files with ESLint |\n| **Lint & auto-fix** | `pnpm run lint-fix` | Lints and auto-fixes where possible |\n\n---\n\n## Summary\n\nThis is a **Vue 3 + Vite** starter template using **pnpm** as its package manager. The typical day-to-day workflow looks like:\n\n```bash\n# One-time setup\npnpm install\n\n# Start developing\npnpm run dev\n\n# Before committing — lint and test\npnpm run lint\npnpm run test:unit\n\n# Production build\npnpm run build\n```", "additional_kwargs": {"refusal": null}, "response_metadata": {"token_usage": {"completion_tokens": 469, "prompt_tokens": 5164, "total_tokens": 5633, "completion_tokens_details": {"accepted_prediction_tokens": null, "audio_tokens": 0, "reasoning_tokens": 21, "rejected_prediction_tokens": null, "image_tokens": 0}, "prompt_tokens_details": {"audio_tokens": 0, "cached_tokens": 4672, "cache_write_tokens": 0, "video_tokens": 0}, "cost": 0, "is_byok": true, "cost_details": {"upstream_inference_cost": 0.0002132816, "upstream_inference_prompt_cost": 8.19616e-05, "upstream_inference_completions_cost": 0.00013132}}, "model_provider": "openai", "model_name": "xiaomi/mimo-v2.5-20260422", "system_fingerprint": null, "id": "gen-1780871225-huezcmaaeat6R5jnNi0v", "finish_reason": "stop", "logprobs": null}, "type": "ai", "name": null, "id": "lc_run--019ea432-604d-7e23-a3e1-8ea8ce5d0713-0", "tool_calls": [], "invalid_tool_calls": [], "usage_metadata": {"input_tokens": 5164, "output_tokens": 469, "total_tokens": 5633, "input_token_details": {"audio": 0, "cache_read": 4672}, "output_token_details": {"audio": 0, "reasoning": 21}}}}]}}}
